suggest that climate change may instead be playing
the dominant role \\\{[$\backslash$\\}Emanuel, 2005; Webster et
al., 2005$\backslash$\\{]\}.Using a formal statistical analysis
to separate the estimated influences of
anthropogenic climate change from possible natural
cyclical influences, this article presents results
