space objective analysis, is applied to the
reconstruction of gridded Pacific Ocean Basin sea
surface temperature (SST) from coral stable isotope
(delta(18)O) data for the period 1607-1990. In this
approach we seek to reconstruct only the leading
modes of large-scale variability which are both
observed in the modern climate and resolved in the
