analyses among the four algorithms that were
tested. Based on these results, the OI technique was
used to create monthly gridded analyses of
precipitation over the global land areas for the
53-yr period from 1948 to 2000. In addition, some
diagnostic investigations of the seasonal and
interannual variability of large-scale precipitation
