   abstract = {6 Key Points: 7 • Explainable Artificial Intelligence methods capture relevant large-scale quantities 8 to predict convective activity. 9 • Mid-level ω shows stronger relation to overall convective activity than to its de-10 gree of organisation. 11 • High degrees of convective organisation in Darwin can occur in both very dry and 12 moist environments. Abstract 14 Deep moist convection is responsible for a large fraction of rainfall in the tropics, but 15 the interaction between deep convection and the large-scale atmosphere remains poorly 16 understood. Here we apply machine learning techniques to examine relationships between 17},
